{"body": "Yep, and when default_asset_host_protocol is left at its default nil value, the assets will use protocol-relative urls if there isn't a request in scope, as would be the case in precompiled js/css : \r\n\r\n```ruby\r\n    def default_protocol\r\n      @config.default_asset_host_protocol || (has_request? ? :request : :relative)\r\n    end\r\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2777928", "created_at": "2011-11-17T16:16:02Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3660#issuecomment-2777928", "updated_at": "2011-11-17T16:16:02Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3660, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/jdelStrother", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/a9e5ce6f28587baa2a566eb4f2d76c13?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F269d837afada308dd4aeab28ca2d57e4.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/received_events", "gravatar_id": "a9e5ce6f28587baa2a566eb4f2d76c13", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "jdelStrother", "type": "User", "id": 2377, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523833d0bd3543c15100fa8f"}, "id": 2777928, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3660"}
